---
// Custom / bespoke tile development service
---

<section class="custom section" id="custom">
  <div class="custom__grid container">
    <div class="custom__text">
      <h2 class="section-title custom__title">Custom Made Tiles</h2>
      <p class="custom__sub">Tailored ceramic solutions for unique projects</p>

      <p>
        Magna Cerámica also offers custom-made tile development services,
        connecting clients with specialized manufacturers for bespoke ceramic
        tiles, mosaics, and special pieces.
      </p>
      <p>
        From specific formats and finishes to decorative mosaics or
        made-to-measure ceramic elements, we help bring custom project
        requirements to life through our network of trusted Spanish producers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <figure class="custom__media">
      <img
        src="/img/custom-tiles.jpg"
        alt="Custom made ceramic tiles and mosaics"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .custom {
    background: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .custom__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .custom__title {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .custom__sub {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .custom__text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .custom__media img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .custom__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
